'''Rov''' was a religious [[Priest/Legends|title]] employed on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ventooine/Legends|Ventooine]]. It was used to denote the highest ranking members of the church on Ventooine. The only known Rov was [[Vetter Piin]] who helped end the rule of the [[Satab]]s. During the height of the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], Rov Piin took to caring for a shrine built in honor of [[Han Solo/Legends|Han Solo]] who helped kill the [[Satab (individual)|last of the Satabs]].

